-- M6 slice 5 parity fixture: explicit BREACH with BY / BECAUSE clauses.
-- Forces the LEST branch to surface a structured BREACH record so we
-- can lock the {BREACH: {by, because}} wire shape against jl4-service.

DECLARE Party IS ONE OF `the borrower`
DECLARE `Repay Action` IS ONE OF `repay loan`

@export default repayment with structured breach
GIVETH A DEONTIC Party `Repay Action`
`repayment contract` MEANS
    PARTY `the borrower`
    MUST `repay loan`
    WITHIN 30
    HENCE FULFILLED
    LEST BREACH BY `the borrower` BECAUSE "loan was not repaid in time"
